name-collision.message.zh: 无法添加到家族中，因为 '{0}' 对象有一个名为 [b]{1}[/b] 的实例变量、行为或滤镜，该名称已经在家族 '{2}' 中使用。请先重命名其中的项目然后重试。
name-collision.message.en: The object type cannot be added to the family, because '{0}' has an instance variable, behavior or effect named [b]{1}[/b], and the family '{2}' already has something using this name. Rename one of the items involved and try again.
